# Normalize every text file to LF, repo-wide. core.autocrlf=true on Windows was
# producing phantom line-ending-only diffs (first seen on .env.example, whose
# rewriter hook .claude/hooks/env-example-sync.js writes LF and byte-compares;
# the same class hit other files). text=auto leaves binaries untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
